Titolo: Rising Storm 2: Vietnam

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Rising Storm 2: Vietnam is a tactical first-person shooter video game developed by Antimatter Games and Tripwire Interactive and is co-published by Tripwire Interactive and Iceberg Interactive. It is a direct sequel to 2013's Rising Storm and is set during the Vietnam War, placing emphasis on asymmetric gameplay. The game was released worldwide for Microsoft Windows through digital distribution platform Steam on May 30, 2017.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
